# Whitelist approach: exclude everything, then include what the build needs.
*

# Workspace root
!Cargo.toml
!Cargo.lock

# Rust workspace members
!rust/
rust/**/target/

# Proto definitions (needed by exomonad-proto build.rs)
!proto/

# Vendored Rust dependencies (acp-rust-sdk)
!vendor/

# Haskell WASM guest sources
!haskell/
!cabal.project.wasm
!flake.nix
!flake.lock

# Role definitions + shared lib (needed for WASM build)
!.exo/roles/
!.exo/lib/

# try-exomonad (bootstrap script)
!try-exomonad/
